propriate.", "q1r": 4, "q2": "The information provided clear and detailed. Have left a lot of personal information to prove the authenticity of the project. The people who carry out the project are experienced, well qualified. I am also a student of Vietnam National University, Ho Chi Minh, although not in the same city, but in the same training place. I know better than anyone to be a lecturer in this environment is very difficult, must be really nice. ", "q2r": 4, "assessor": "z_assessor_756", "no_vca": 18, "ne": 1, "ng": 11, "nfo": 6, "vca_o": 1}, {"q0": "I strongly agree this challenge is critical to achieve Cardano's decentralize mission. \r\n\r\nThe proposal addressed the key concern of of Vietnamese communitive. The more stake pool operates, the more decentralize the network will be. Bringing the renewable energy sources to operate the stake pool also great idea for sustainable development.\r\n\r\nIt would be great if proposer provide more information about how many percent of stake pool in Vietnam as compared with cardano's total stake pool then voters can image how can this proposal can impact to Vietnamese community.", "q0r": 5, "q1": "This proposal is very likely to be successful based on the definition of success set out in the plan. The proposers are currently Stake Pool Operator then they have all the experience in running it. \r\n\r\nThe budget is clear and reasonable for each items. The milestones are realistic and feasible. \r\n\r\nThe only point I would add is a deeper analysis about the solar solutions: ie: the average of energy consumption for each stake pool per month. If it is a big amount then the solar energy can help, bare in mind that the solar panel and battery are also not environment friendly.", "q1r": 5, "q2": "\"The proposal includes a roadmap with targets and a plan extending to June 2022 and the mass adoption will be consider in next fund which show a carefull approach of proposers. \r\n\r\nThe proposal shows detailed steps, milestone and deliverables that will be simple to check if the project is running on schedule. \r\n\r\nOn the material to run SPO in Vietnamese (including the documents as well as the video), i would suggest proposer provide KPIs for the audience reach (ie: subscriber on youtube channel, website visitor increase...)\"", "q2r": 5, "assessor": "z_assessor_819", "no_vca": 17, "ne": 4, "ng": 12, "nfo": 1, "vca_o": 1}, {"q0": "In my opinion this proposal could improve the stakeholder participations in the Cardano community Stake Pool Operators and the developer work on cardano blockchain.\nThe proposal have the correct mix from building and deploying a new kind of stake pool (bare metal vs cloud), ecological solar power, passion for creating educational contents\u2026\nHowever the objective of the proposal is interesting and it\u2019s good for growth the Vietnamese community, but I think it's important to enrich the proposal with other kind of support for SPOs, because only building a new stake pool doesn\u2019t enough to improve economics for Vietnamese communities.", "q0r": 4, "q1": "The proposer team has very good experience, because they are very well experienced Stake pool operators member. \nThe metrics for the assessment are given, so it\u2019s possible to assess what the proposer wants to do and the success of his actions. Roadmap and milestones are described (date, actions, kpi).", "q1r": 4, "q2": "Roadmap and milestones are basically described. The budget\u2019s information provided is described. There aren\u2019t a lot of KPI to identify the proposal goal, but only deliverables. There are some details how the budget is going to be spent, also I'm trying to discover attachment to deep dive the solution. Futhermore there are basic information to asses.", "q2r": 4, "assessor": "z_assessor_114", "no_vca": 19, "ne": 1, "ng": 17, "nfo": 1, "vca_o": 1}], "solution": "\u6280\u8853\u8005\u3067\u306a\u304f\u3066\u3082\u3067\u304d\u308b\u3088\u3046\u306b\u3001\u30b9\u30c6\u30a4\u30af\u30d7\u30fc\u30eb\u30ac\u30a4\u30c9\u306e\u8a2d\u5b9a\u3068\u64cd\u4f5c\u3092\u7c21\u7d20\u5316\u3059\u308b\u3002\u30bb\u30c3\u30c8\u30a2\u30c3\u30d7\u6e08\u307f\u306e\u592a\u967d\u5149\u767a\u96fb\u7528\u30b9\u30c6\u30fc\u30af\u30d7\u30fc\u30eb\u6a5f\u5668\u3092\u5e02\u5834\u306b\u63d0\u4f9b\u3059\u308b\u3002", "experience": "\u79c1\u305f\u3061\u306f\u3001SPO\u3067\u3042\u308a\u3001\u6771\u90e8\u30bf\u30a6\u30f3\u30db\u30fc\u30eb\u306e\u30e2\u30c7\u30ec\u30fc\u30bf\u30fc\u3067\u3042\u308a\u3001\u30d6\u30ed\u30c3\u30af\u30c1\u30a7\u30fc\u30f3\u306e\u6280\u8853\u7cbe\u901a\u8005\u3067\u3042\u308a\u3001\u30a8\u30ec\u30af\u30c8\u30ed\u30cb\u30af\u30b9\u3001\u30aa\u30fc\u30c8\u30e1\u30fc\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3\u306e\u5c02\u9580\u5bb6\u3067\u3059\u3002"}